{--when we use this for link css in google show href source like this:'css/style.css'--}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css"> this is relative path


{--i want that href link show with domain name like:http://localhost:8000/css/style.css   then we use asset() method--}

<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/style.css') }}"> it is absolute path

{--if we want to add font file js file then for absolute path we use asset() }

